title: What Remains of Edith Finch-HI2U
description:
What Remains of Edith Finch (c) Annapurna Interactive

Release 25/04/2017

Protection: Steam
Game Size: 1 DISC

Game Type: Adventure, Indie [RELEASE NOTES]

What Remains of Edith Finch is a collection of strange tales
about a family in Washington state. As Edith, you'll explore the
colossal Finch house, searching for stories as she explores her
family history and tries to figure out why she's the last one in
her family left alive 


[INSTALL NOTES] 

1 Mount / burn image 
2 Install 
3 Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files 
4 Play game 
5 If U like it, buy it!
